    <h1>Lead Magnet</h1>
    <p class="description">A free, high-value resource offered in exchange for a visitor's contact information. The bridge between anonymous traffic and a real pipeline — when matched to content, lead magnets convert at <strong>20-40%</strong> versus a 2-3% site baseline.</p>
